      "hintIndex": 1,
      "text": "这次有三个声音！链式合成器可以处理多个输入。把三个声音都连上吧——/k/ 接第一个口，/ae/ 接第二个，/t/ 接第三个。",
      "textEn": "Three sounds this time! The chain blender can handle multiple inputs. Connect all three — /k/ to port 1, /ae/ to port 2, /t/ to port 3.",
