  "introText": "这是一台更高级的合成器——链式合成器。它不止有两个输入端口，而是三个！左边有三颗声音水晶：/k/、/ae/、/t/。如果把它们按正确的顺序全部连到合成器，会发生什么？一个更长的'超级声音'？",
  "introTextEn": "A more advanced blender — the chain blender — has three input ports! Three sound crystals sit on the left: /k/, /ae/, /t/. Connect all three in the right order — what 'super-sound' will emerge?",
  "victoryText": "合成器输出了 /kaet/！三个独立的声音碎片串联后变成了一个完整的'超级声音'。等一下……/k/ + /ae/ + /t/ = /kaet/……这不正是一个古老的'单词'吗？！原来：单词就是声音的序列！",
  "victoryTextEn": "The blender produced /kaet/! Three independent fragments chained together become a complete 'super-sound.' Wait... /k/ + /ae/ + /t/ = /kaet/... isn't this an ancient 'word'?! Words are sequences of sounds!",
